{"tid":480632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺啲購物網站收交易手續費好小家","createTime":"2017-11-26T10:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T10:58:56.000Z","uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a556203e81299b283eb74addd7e0a851ea94b4d5","tid":480632,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"多咗付款方法係為咗方便買家畀錢, 即係吸引你喺佢嗰道買嘢<br />\n畀人可以信用卡/PayPal畀錢, 但係收返買家手續費<br />\n明明慳咗人手, 反而銀行過數/到貨付款呢啲要多啲人力嘅嘢就唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁即係其實個手續費根本就係信用卡公司/PayPal向佢哋收嘅<br />\n但係又想賺到盡, 要買家自己負擔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c07989ee31a7d953b08c6d4a139a40936d2b09","tid":480632,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"用者自付<br />\n<br />\n間鋪話唔收其實已經charge左你"}]}